caption: A young girl wearing a sweatshirt and tall socks stands in a grassy area, holding a rope attached to a large brown horse, with a small fire in the foreground and open land in the background including an older man and his darker brown horse

People enjoy a leisurely walk on a paved pathway in a park. Two of them are middle aged women walking side by side towards the front and two of them are adult individuals walking away. There is a young boy holding a red ball getting ready to kick it. There are benches along the path and on one of them there is an adult woman sitting down with her legs crossed, and another has an old man sitting down taking a phone call with his legs crossed and a black dog besides him staring into the distance. The athlete with the blue jersey seems to be pushing the athlete with a white one to get hold of the ball from her. There are two more athletes in the background from each of the two teams.

A hiker wearing black gear climbs up a steep slope covered with snow using hooks in his hands to pierce through snow. The backdrop shows the snowy trail shining with sunlight, on the left are some plants and mountain rock. At the foreground are a couple of hiking sticks etched in snow.

The most prominent pedestrian is wearing a brown jacket and blue jeans. The middle ground contains an intersection where pedestrians wait to cross in one direction and cross in the. Two cop cars wait for the light to change. A stone building that resembles a fort is behind the intersection, with taller office-style buildings behind them. It looks like New York City.
An Asian man and woman are patronizing a street food vendor with a yellow taxi parked behind them. There is another woman on the left with her face blocked by a tree.

A young woman in knee-high rubber boots and a black long-sleeve shirt with an athletic logo stands in a grassy field, holding a rope in her left hand that is tied to a horse's green bit, on her right. The horse faces toward a firepit in the foreground, along with the woman. In the background, an older white male with a baseball cap, blue shirt, blue jeans, and a lanyard looks toward the fire as well. A horse walks partially off camera to his left. There are logs scattered on the background behind the man and the second horse. Wooden fences are in the far background, and a forest is behind them.

A man in a park talking to his phone with his dog besides him as the dog looks at the camera. The sky looks cloudy and a boy in a red shirt is playing basketball. There also seems to be a venue place at the background.

The other woman has a look of shock on her face with her mouth wide open as she falls down with the ball still in her possession at her right foot. The ball has each pentagon colored white with a black border and each hexagon surrounded in black with a white triangle in the center. They are in a soccer pitch with a red flag in the background representing the edge of the field. There is a woman from the blue team in the right on the back and one from the white team on the left side. Behind them is a black net and behind that there is a bunch of tall bushes completely covering the background.
